%F A281780 a(n) = 1/2*S(n, 4) + 9/2*S(n, 5) + 16*S(n, 6) + 295/12*S(n, 7) + 85/4*S(n, 8) + 49/4*S(n, 9) + 9/2*S(n, 10) + S(n, 11), with S(n, k) = k!*Stirling2(n, k).
%F A281780 From _M. F. Hasler_, Jun 21 2026: (Start)
%F A281780 G.f.: 12*x^4*(1 - 11*x - 5*x^2 - 1860*x^3 + 46974*x^4 - 339229*x^5 + 873730*x^6 + 277200*x^7) / Product_{k=1..11} (1 - k*x).
